{"list":[{"title":"目的","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">观察</span>&alpha;粒子散射现象<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">；了解原子的核式结构模型。</span></span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"原理","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">原子的核式结构模型。</span></span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"器材","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">&alpha;粒子散射器</span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"步骤","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">1.打开开关，从显示器观察在</span>&alpha;粒子前进方向观测到的粒子数<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">；</span></span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">2.沿顺时针或逆时针方向调整观测角度，从显示器观察</span>&alpha;粒子在特定角度下观测到的粒子数<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span></span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">3.在属性中将类型改为</span>&ldquo;原理一&rdquo;，观察&alpha;粒子从原子间通过时的偏转情况；</span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">4.在属性中将类型改为</span>&ldquo;原理二&rdquo;，观察&alpha;粒子从原子核周围通过时的偏转情况。</span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"结论","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">绝大多数</span></span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">&alpha;粒子穿过金箔后，基本上仍沿原来的方向前进，有少数&alpha;粒子发生了大角度偏转，偏转的角度甚至大于<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">90</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">&deg;，再次基础上得到：</span></span></span><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">原子中带正电部分的体积很小，但几乎占有全部质量，电子在正电体的外面运动。</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"补充","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">&alpha;粒子散射是估计核半径的最简单的方法，对于一般的原子核，实验确定的核半径的数量级为<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">10</span></span></span><sup><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">-15</span></span></sup><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">m<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，而整个原子半径的数量级是</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">10</span></span></span><sup><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">-10</span></span></sup><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">m<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，两者相差十万倍之多，原子内部是十分&ldquo;空旷&rdquo;的。</span></span></span></span></span></p>"}],"x":0,"y":0,"width":600,"height":600}